(SEBI Circular: Cybersecurity Resilience Framework) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
0 -30 Td
(Circular No: SEBI/HO/MIRSD/CIR/P/2026/123) Tj
0 -20 Td
(Date: June 29, 2026) Tj
0 -40 Td
(1. Background and Purpose) Tj
0 -20 Td
(In view of the increasing cyber threats, SEBI hereby mandates that all registered) Tj
0 -15 Td
(stock brokers must implement a Cyber Security Resilience Framework (CRF).) Tj
0 -30 Td
(2. Existing Systems Alignment (Compliant Baseline)) Tj
0 -20 Td
(Brokers who have already implemented ISO 27001 standard certification shall) Tj
0 -15 Td
(be deemed compliant with Chapter II of this framework, provided audit reports) Tj
0 -15 Td
(are submitted annually.) Tj
ET
endstream
