stream
BT
/F1 14 Tf
50 780 Td
(3. Modified Requirements (Changed Language)) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
0 -30 Td
(Under the previous guidelines, the Reporting Incident window was 24 hours.) Tj
0 -20 Td
(As per the revised framework, all cyber incidents MUST be reported within) Tj
0 -15 Td
(6 hours of detection to the MIRSD department and CERT-In.) Tj
0 -40 Td
(4. New Obligations (High Risk / Mandatory Compliance)) Tj
0 -20 Td
(Registered stock brokers must establish a dedicated Cyber Security Committee) Tj
0 -15 Td
(headed by a Chief Information Security Officer (CISO). The committee must meet) Tj
0 -15 Td
(at least once every quarter and submit minutes to the Board.) Tj
ET
endstream
