0 -20 Td
(the CISO Appointment Letter, and CERT-In registration proof. All documents) Tj
0 -15 Td
(must be signed by the Compliance Officer and uploaded to the SEBI portal.) Tj
0 -45 Td
(End of Circular. All requirements are effective from August 1, 2026.) Tj
ET
